# check collinearity
household %>% 
  select(Total.Household.Income,Total.Food.Expenditure,Household.Head.Sex,Household.Head.Age,Type.of.Household,Total.Number.of.Family.members,House.Floor.Area,Number.of.bedrooms,Electricity) %>% 
  ggpairs(household)
